{"tid":665083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"而且因為片子不好賣，湊莉久只能參加「超亂交」的企劃","createTime":"2018-05-14T15:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T02:15:41.000Z","uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a24b23209b9927540ce77da47c73b33bfe4ca038","tid":665083,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"而且因為片子不好賣，湊莉久於如今市場低迷不振，她只能點頭參加「超亂交」的企劃。<br />\n<br />\n不過，並不是每一位女優都能接受這樣的「重口味」，有些女優可能無法在鏡頭前自然展現自己，總會失聲痛哭。因此，只能佩服湊莉久這些女優帶來如此專業的表現與敬業，在市場不景氣的情況下，要殺出一條血路，真是越來越不容易了。"},{"pid":"6c88b2b20f8ec5ac545a79c2b64efe268ffab744","tid":665083,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a10ba805d49fe69dfc75f1ba2ab95bbab8bb27","tid":665083,"uid":67225,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"好想睇av女優失聲痛哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391dee27e9647a68641706a56787c828605fc9c5","tid":665083,"uid":168534,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"湊莉久好樣衰"},{"pid":"394ae89148c7f5f65d196f114d20815f5a0fb7fa","tid":665083,"uid":166413,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"臭痢狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fada9d67002b6618bf98efec16fceb32c4758ff1","tid":665083,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e38f23140d8f5a569673a9d99679abd8c7a6b12","tid":665083,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:46:31.000Z","msg":"七孔齊發?"},{"pid":"72f147b3fe3a3720c898841e80b4f1ab20dc